id=termux_nix_selinux
name=Termux Nix SELinux transition
version=v1
versionCode=1
author=nixcfg
description=Grants the exec-based domain transition that lets su -Z re-enter Termux's app domain without the zygote seccomp filter, so native Nix (glibc) binaries can run. The sepolicy.rule is generated at install from Termux's live SELinux domain.
